  "url": "https://www.tamilmirror.lk/\u0bae\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd/\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd-\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd-\u0b85\u0bb4-\u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd-\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0ba4-\u0ba4\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8/76-299696",
  "time_ut": 1656933739,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb4,  \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0ba4 \u0ba4\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The children cry because of hunger, the father cries in the middle of the street",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 37-year-old father of two was panting in the middle of the main town of Hemmathagama, saying that he could not watch his children cry for milk in the absence of food.",
        "Seeing him holding a flag and crying, the police, traders and people in the city bought him the food he needed.",
        "He works as a mason and has a 7-year-old daughter and a 13-year-old son. His wife is unemployed. Due to the economic crisis, the price of cement has increased. Due to this, he is not properly employed.",
        "The banner read, \"The Masons have been patient enough, reduce the prices of goods and give relief to the poor.\"",
        "A 7-year-old girl cries for milk. Not just milk for the children, there is nothing to eat three meals a day for the entire family. I am unable to raise my children because I am unable to get a job,\u201d he said.",
        "The police went near the man who was sitting on the main road and questioned him. After that, the people gathered there forgot the caste, religion and language barriers and did their best to help. With the help received, the police, public and traders got the necessary items for the person."
      ],
